Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人真的没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天不是还要去做家教吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.49,0:02:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总得先休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.68,0:02:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能来看正式演出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是排练
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说错了是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做事的原则是边探讨边推进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排练也应该以这种方式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也都这么觉得  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说白了  就是没干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你搞的这些夸张的玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是上一辈的嬉皮士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不是说过设计按照画的样子来就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是参考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你居然原封不动地做出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导演的风格最近一直都在变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不跟着我们的步调来商量怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种画太幼稚  根本看不懂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之改改吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  幸亏公演不是明天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又不想去  夕凪的学祭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去见由绮也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗  我前两天又…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了  我做什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间不够时就要用人海战术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽仓小姐是指挥官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和这个废物该做些什么  请下令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座敷童子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是座敷童子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在问由绮你的哥哥回来了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮是那位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮酱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮酱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮酱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝这边看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮酱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  时间差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不唱歌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不唱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新曲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱首新曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没练习多久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为补偿  有一件事要告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸  美咲她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没睡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来打算叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但泽仓小姐说  就让你睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你参加展销会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么展销啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演出节目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扮演布朗神父
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得吗  布朗宁诗集
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从美咲那里借来的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  福尔摩斯的助手…对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿上帝保佑你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道美咲在哪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你说的是要加敬称的那个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  Happys来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是叫人吓了一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是  风头全被抢过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有人气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…由绮  森川由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对对  由绮酱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小八
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小响
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  能不能别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我签名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊抱歉  可以不要拍照吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮她…来了这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期六你准备做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是在学校里转转
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有认真地在排练了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上我们做的那些衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:08:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真地在做了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真地…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君说话的方式好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是正式的排练嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲没来看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  收拾好就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是  都没怎么睡过嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  多亏了你们睡得很香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一定要来看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好的印在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是给你们添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是客气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然见外起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连你父亲都过来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天结束后会去感谢  顺便打扫下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦帮我转告他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了呢…终于
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了  应该不会再有这样的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  再有这样的事随时可以找我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在忙吗  那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  已经做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了错了  那边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计是…不会满座的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那边的布景
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开场后演员入场时怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点拆掉  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最靠后的角落里就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人的位置都不能想想办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没睡醒吗  美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观众席是为观众而存在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也算是个工作人员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然总是在需要你的时候不见人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去边上看吧  不许捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不可能坚持到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好心到通宵帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好心帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你没问题哦  自己去观众席上看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,票到接待处去买  成人票700日元一张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田丸  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲  我去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不跟你废话了  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上要开演了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啦美咲  我去买票…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！不能听任田丸摆布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说我去买了后把票给美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不就谁也不能多嘴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那藤井君怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天也稍微看了点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天就不必特意再看了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意跟我一起看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就买两张  弄两个位子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好想想  田丸不允许我坐在观众席
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也不会卖你两张的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就请跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲  那难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二楼的坐席现在没有开放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看台被当成了杂物房
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年准备学祭的时候被叫去拿腰鼓的时候发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最里面的墙后  有照明用的小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的话  就不会被人打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉兴奋起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首铃  还有5分钟就开演了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大探险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  之后只要直走就行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  终点近在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,序章只能放弃了  田丸的独演要持续一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天看了哦  好像时代剧一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时代剧？我好像要发烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  既然决定了  就稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那是？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:16:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝  我正好口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人怀念啊  这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得吗  日川町的那个电影院
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三映馆？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  正好就是这种气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在光束下  飘着烟尘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们碰见过吧  美咲一个人去那的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  藤井君是跟由绮一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮那家伙  一看到美咲就跑过去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人一起亲亲热热
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话我挺嫉妒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是被她缠着  热得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候明明也是冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  还能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟美咲一起  看到各种各样的美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你看到了很多弱点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:18:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢的学姐  而且偶尔成为只属于我的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很尊敬你  跟由绮一样想永远跟着你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  彰不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彰对美咲的心意跟我们不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然说起这个来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲  你对彰怎么看？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是现在该说的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  谁在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲对不起  我竟然说出这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当心那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里痛？脚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  太黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭到了吗  要是骨折就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我马上去叫救护车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  留在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  留在这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我说那么奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  早就决定好了…变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美…咲？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四幕  肮脏而邪恶的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起因是诗集  演剧剧本  设计
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误解  妄想不断膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒学弟的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至嫉妒她的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛她  欺骗她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道学弟的朋友的心意  却不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲  不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:19:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为学弟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对学弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把学弟…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别回答我的告白  因为你有由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你根本没想过我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你放心吧  错的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗我？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没发现吗  这都是我安排的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能让我的剧本登上舞台而利用你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肮脏而邪恶的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说的只有这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  耽误了你的时间  你可以走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲  我喜欢你  很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢你  所以你走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  那呆子在那种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.85,0:21:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.49,0:21:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.98,0:21:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲  …
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.23,0:22:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终幕  接受惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.42,0:24:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十页  独角戏之所以空虚  并非因为只有一个演员
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.00,0:24:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是观众的目光  刺得好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.35,0:24:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White  Album
